author: Jonathan Barrett
title: Australian authorities take cluster approach to contain coronavirus
description: Australian authorities will open a pop-up coronavirus testing clinic next to Sydney's Bondi Beach on Wednesday as health workers try to contain clusters of infections across the country.
content:
SYDNEY (Reuters) - Australian authorities will open a pop-up coronavirus testing clinic next to Sydney’s Bondi Beach on Wednesday as health workers try to contain clusters of infections across the country.
